{"tid":630003,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［好燥］鋤大Dee之計法","createTime":"2018-04-15T07:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T10:59:20.000Z","uid":36531,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d2c599bf93537f632cdfd86e10ff8435d3c48abb","tid":630003,"uid":36531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:51:44.000Z","msg":"話明鋤大Dee, 2 係最大，單牌順序為：<br />\n2, A, K, Q, J, 10, 9, 8, 7, 6, 5, 4, 3<br />\n<br />\n花式順序為：<br />\n黑葵扇，紅心，黑梅花，紅階磚<br />\n<br />\n由話事人（上輪其他人全pass), 出牌，下家一定要跟佢牌型，如：<br />\n<br />\n單隻（出一隻）<br />\nPair (兩隻同數字）<br />\n蛇（唔理花，五隻連續順序嘅牌，A為終點及起點⋯⋯最細34568，最大12346，JQKA2並不存在）<br />\n花 （五隻同花式，大小先計字，後計花）<br />\n夫佬 （三隻同字 搭對 pair, 計三隻同子大細）<br />\n同花順（同花既蛇，計第一隻）<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------<br />\n好喇，廢話講完<br />\n呢度有兩對花<br />\n紅心<br />\nA 6 5 4 3 <br />\n叫做 煙(A)花<br />\n<br />\n黑葵<br />\nK Q J 10 8<br />\n叫做 King (K)花<br />\n<br />\n一打出黎就知煙花大啦， 理得你葵扇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果第一隻相同，會先比較之後一隻數字，如5隻一樣先計花<br />\n<br />\n就咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16eccfabe98496902b6c2e9675355e40c332eb07","tid":630003,"uid":139150,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2c599bf93537f632cdfd86e10ff8435d3c48abb","tid":630003,"uid":36531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:51:44.000Z","msg":"話明鋤大Dee, 2 係最大，單牌順序為：<br />\n2, A, K, Q, J, 10, 9, 8, 7, 6, 5, 4, 3<br />\n<br />\n花式順序為：<br />\n黑葵扇，紅心，黑梅花，紅階磚<br />\n<br />\n由話事人（上輪其他人全pass), 出牌，下家一定要跟佢牌型，如：<br />\n<br />\n單隻（出一隻）<br />\nPair (兩隻同數字）<br />\n蛇（唔理花，五隻連續順序嘅牌，A為終點及起點⋯⋯最細34568，最大12346，JQKA2並不存在）<br />\n花 （五隻同花式，大小先計字，後計花）<br />\n夫佬 （三隻同字 搭對 pair, 計三隻同子大細）<br />\n同花順（同花既蛇，計第一隻）<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------<br />\n好喇，廢話講完<br />\n呢度有兩對花<br />\n紅心<br />\nA 6 5 4 3 <br />\n叫做 煙(A)花<br />\n<br />\n黑葵<br />\nK Q J 10 8<br />\n叫做 King (K)花<br />\n<br />\n一打出黎就知煙花大啦， 理得你葵扇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果第一隻相同，會先比較之後一隻數字，如5隻一樣先計花<br />\n<br />\n就咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:57:10.000Z","msg":"Straight (also known as a snake in Cantonese or mokke in Malaysia): Any 5 cards in a sequence (but not all of the same suit). Rank is determined by the value of the biggest card, with the suit used only as a tie-breaker. Therefore 3-4-5-6-7 &lt; 2-3-4-5-6, since 2 is considered the largest card in the 2-3-4-5-6 straight. <span style=\"color: red;\">The largest straight is 2-3-4-5-6, second A-2-3-4-5, third 10-J-Q-K-A </span>while the smallest straight is 3-4-5-6-7.<br />\n<br />\nFrom wiki. 樓主點睇？"},{"pid":"a0d24d274c919992abbef968b676831d112e2192","tid":630003,"uid":73565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T08:07:38.000Z","msg":"蛇先最麻煩 屌到底A2345定23456定34567定AKQJ10最大／最細"},{"pid":"a27de06972fc107f87a04d06bd77054613ae8175","tid":630003,"uid":14910,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T08:11:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55db1ee5513f28fd935aad6c28ee05494852fefb","tid":630003,"uid":65593,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T08:12:09.000Z","msg":"打花計字先 重叫唔叫打花<br />\n利申次次鋤dee之前一定問清楚點計法先玩"},{"pid":"067971add853d87dc35f3d76fbefa41836108cc3","tid":630003,"uid":44956,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T08:13:40.000Z","msg":"玩開23456最細 10JQKA最大 A同2永遠連唔埋"},{"pid":"ae39724931e0cf48bcf6ecb03b500c8b12c4f4b5","tid":630003,"uid":44956,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"067971add853d87dc35f3d76fbefa41836108cc3","tid":630003,"uid":44956,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T08:13:40.000Z","msg":"玩開23456最細 10JQKA最大 A同2永遠連唔埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T08:14:49.000Z","msg":"花就先計數字 5個數字都一樣先計花"},{"pid":"7f1cdc12aeb3811b989d841908d928d6d144178d","tid":630003,"uid":142222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"06797